Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.03,0:00:25.36,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Macross Galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.18,0:00:32.52,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先于Frontier数年启航的21号巨型移民船团
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.52,0:00:35.58,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由大企业设计制定方案
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.74,0:00:39.05,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无保留地投入各种先进技术
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.37,0:00:43.02,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航海过程中也继续发展技术
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.44,0:00:46.50,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在电脑工程学和植入技术上成果卓越
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.67,0:00:51.01,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一跃成为少数拥有高科技能力的船团之一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.35,0:00:55.11,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但即使是Galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.38,0:00:57.54,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Vajra的攻击下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.17,0:00:59.28,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求援 求援
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.36,0:01:01.75,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些臭虫们爬上了主岛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.76,0:01:02.53,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.06,0:01:13.91,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船体各部件无异常
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:15.55,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,De-fold成功
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.19,0:01:20.66,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认本舰前方02方位达尔特弗和卡利托斯的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.08,0:01:22.10,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示影像
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.67,0:01:25.53,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好严重
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:29.87,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 我们的首要任务虽然是救援幸存舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.07,0:01:32.58,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其同等 甚至更重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.67,0:01:36.46,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集Vajra的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.06,0:01:39.79,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不代表新统合军
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.93,0:01:43.04,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是总统阁下的要求吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:46.16,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以这样理解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.16,0:01:49.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢速前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.11,0:01:53.75,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会留意的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.66,0:01:56.77,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰 战斗准备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:38.00,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 投入吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:45.32,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M5和6 M5…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:48.56,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多没来？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.17,0:03:49.07,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到我的告别演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.51,0:03:52.13,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间虽然短暂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:54.97,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很庆幸能认识Frontier的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:01.11,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:05.17,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生许多事 让大家操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:07.48,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢丽尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:11.54,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:13.37,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚像平常那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.57,0:04:15.45,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飙出Macross的速度来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.01,0:04:16.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.16,0:04:19.78,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我的歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:51.03,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骷髅队长向各机通话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:52.63,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是给军队打头阵的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:54.90,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便还要收集Vajra的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.09,0:04:56.97,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试作型空间跳跃通信诱导系统
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:04:57.65,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,状态良好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:00.79,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有它应该不会再被Vajra扰乱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:02.00,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:03.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:05.39,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你尽可能靠后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:08.18,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我也能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:09.96,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:14.16,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那先跟上我再说 不许走远
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:17.10,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:18.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全机 Planet Dance
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:22.04,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙 路哈尼 彼特洛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:22.79,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.67,0:05:29.90,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先走一步 米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:34.40,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别又因为看不见我就哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:36.59,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真多嘴 葛兰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:38.83,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候的事纠缠不休
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.17,0:05:55.04,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:02.98,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别发呆 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:03.83,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:23.74,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么笨重的重装型
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.63,0:06:32.91,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能被它甩掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:46.48,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尝尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:06.91,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡纳莉亚 干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:07.79,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:11.01,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dabind01向达尔特弗通话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.19,0:07:12.40,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借甲板一用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:14.92,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是达尔特弗 请脚下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.49,0:07:22.46,ENG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs44}Konig Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.49,0:07:22.46,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(635,655)}怪兽之王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:25.18,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主甲板固定 抗冲击防护
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.31,0:07:27.02,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开工
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:30.55,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dabind01开始迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:33.07,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想死的人都撤出我的视野
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:34.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Konig Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:37.11,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物退散
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.14,0:07:53.20,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.84,0:07:57.46,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别发呆 先保护损伤严重的卡利托斯撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.09,0:07:59.01,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:06.22,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认与Frontier空间跳跃数据链接
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:11.42,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空间跳跃通信 数据链接状态良好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:13.10,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,延迟为+40
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.42,0:08:16.67,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一攻击部队 开始与Vajra交战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.13,0:08:18.75,ENG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs44}Hyperion&Prometheus
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.13,0:08:18.75,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(512,655)}土卫七
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.13,0:08:18.75,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(730,655)}土卫十六
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.88,0:08:20.72,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二攻击队正在部署中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:23.49,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡利托斯 受损率45%
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:24.65,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负伤者众多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:26.43,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优先派遣救援部队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:38.51,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屏幕的切换不好 查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.98,0:08:40.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.17,0:08:42.37,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占优势
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.74,0:08:44.39,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Frontier的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:46.11,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似比想象的优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.16,0:08:47.17,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:48.40,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.57,0:08:53.20,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 又到线路上偷听了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.48,0:08:56.19,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:08:59.99,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 几乎是现场直播
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.99,0:09:11.35,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多 怎么还不来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:13.58,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么精彩的演出
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:18.10,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.96,0:09:25.80,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实应该亲口告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:27.08,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些难以启齿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.11,0:09:30.24,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作原因 今天回不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:31.75,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.16,0:09:36.10,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一定会遵守约定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:38.01,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:41.27,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:44.25,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那阿鲁多也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:51.01,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢的那位飞行员似乎也很卖力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:53.21,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别误会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:56.25,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我担心的是Galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:01.56,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且飞行员的工作如果是战斗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.63,0:10:05.24,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的工作就是唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:09.86,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡利托斯 正撤离战斗区域
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:12.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离空间跳跃安全范围还有450
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.93,0:10:19.75,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这种空间断层的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.79,0:10:21.37,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能更早逃离
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:29.13,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避开 彼特洛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:47.96,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:54.53,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡利托斯被炸沉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:56.64,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸存者…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.08,0:10:57.93,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.23,0:11:00.77,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,径直穿越了空间断层
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:04.67,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:08.83,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Vajra的战舰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.65,0:11:10.76,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:16.75,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们的母舰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:19.44,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SK-3 卢卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.46,0:11:20.24,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太靠前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.39,0:11:21.27,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:23.19,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是必须对它…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:26.05,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光束发射器？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.17,0:11:28.60,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这种空间跳跃能量反应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:31.80,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是空间跳跃牵引器？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.93,0:11:32.69,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:42.56,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SK-3 丢失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.79,0:11:43.92,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SK-1 发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:45.85,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢卡被敌人吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.28,0:11:47.35,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.38,0:11:48.42,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被击落了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:49.22,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:52.65,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那艘船俘虏并吞掉了卢卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:55.24,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢卡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:18.41,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到最后一首了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.97,0:12:20.84,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也必须和大家告别了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:22.36,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然时间过得很快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.66,0:12:24.59,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却留下了美好的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:27.97,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在广阔的银河中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:30.70,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知能不能重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:36.22,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:38.76,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.93,0:12:40.97,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢丽尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.75,0:12:44.98,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢丽尔别哭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.55,0:12:52.15,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.19,0:12:54.14,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:08.42,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢丽尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:27.60,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家听我说几句
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:31.59,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一首歌想为某个人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:35.30,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…是为某些人而唱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:39.57,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为在远方奋战的将士们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:42.97,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:45.87,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢丽尔小姐明知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:54.31,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知道…却
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.16,0:14:00.72,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你…也能一起唱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:13.05,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家 我爱你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:23.15,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从绝望中启程的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.20,0:14:31.32,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有耳边的风声为我们送行…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.24,0:14:38.15,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.18,0:14:40.62,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来 你一个人能干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:42.73,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:45.49,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手可是艘刺猬一样的船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.59,0:14:47.60,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他刺猬不刺猬的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:51.61,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要钻进肚子里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:06.33,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太莽撞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.56,0:15:07.82,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:09.41,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡纳莉亚 米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.99,0:15:20.74,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么机体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:47.80,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.82,0:15:49.72,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:51.61,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜算如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:53.47,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是只乌龟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.54,0:15:54.76,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:58.33,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 根据SK-3收集的数据模拟运算
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:00.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最大战斗速度时我们略胜一筹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:02.47,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:04.13,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各部门无异常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:07.59,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改装后首次使用 应该能行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:10.02,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.14,0:16:12.70,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据对方炮击模式编成了回避程序
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.97,0:16:14.56,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导航请交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:16.57,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:18.54,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贸然出击太过危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:20.90,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算飞行员被困敌人舰内
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:22.15,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.23,0:16:23.42,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们逃跑的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:25.54,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达尔特弗的乘员会被全灭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:28.25,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Galaxy也会安危难料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:29.00,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:35.04,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛拉斯中尉 你传达的总统要求是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:40.19,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还有实现它的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:49.01,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.69,0:16:58.85,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自相残杀？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:00.70,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:02.38,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.27,0:17:09.61,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Quarter向起飞的所有部队通话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:12.76,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰即将开始对Vajra母舰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:14.54,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,采取近距离格斗战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:16.03,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格斗战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.83,0:17:18.24,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于闪亮登场了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:21.41,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸位全力保护达尔特弗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:24.02,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大的猎物归我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.81,0:17:27.22,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰 Transformation
